\na discrete set, seems in general as efficient as the continuous bounded one.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jan 2022 16:59:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 15:40:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-11"}
