lds an entanglement\nentropy determined by the distribution functions and increases upon unitary\ntime evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jan 2022 21:05:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Mar 2022 20:57:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-16"}
