. This is in contrast to the large-scale\nmagnetic fields obtained from ZDI investigations, performed using the same\nobservations. While the large-scale field might look significantly different.\nThis indicates that the efficiency of the magnetic dynamo is comparable for the\ncomponents of the two binaries, because most energy is carreid by the small\nscale fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jan 2022 13:22:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-23"}
